You're developing software for a smart home system.

There are different kinds of smart devices, such as:

Smart Lights

Smart Thermostats

Smart Speakers

All smart devices:
Can be turned on/off

Can connect to WiFi

Can receive software updates

But some devices also:
Play media (e.g., Smart Speaker)

Adjust temperature (e.g., Smart Thermostat)

Change color (e.g., Smart Lights)

